<P>
 An Orange County chapter of the Dance Resource Center of Greater Los Angeles 
has been formed to develop audiences and provide support for local dance 
professionals. Dance events in the county will be listed in the DRC's bimonthly 
newsletter, and chapter organizers plan to offer performances and 
lecture-demonstrations in such easily accessible public places as parks where, 
as choreographer Deborah Brockus notes, "dance doesn't normally exist." Basic 
membership is $20 and includes the newsletter. (310) 531-8949 or (213) 
622-0815. 
