</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Friends and supporters of the Artists Rights Foundation can get satisfaction 
and donate funds by purchasing prime seats at the Rolling Stones' Oct. 21 show 
at the Rose Bowl. 
</P>
<P>
