<DOCNO> LA101194-0076 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 087525 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 11, 1994, Tuesday, Ventura West Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 2; Column 2 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
