investigation is still going on," Huntington Beach Police Sgt. Chuck Thomas 
said. 
</P>
<P>
 Police do not know when Fleck was incarcerated and could only say he had been 
in prison for several months. 
</P>
<P>
 Lawson and Wells were found by police lying next to each other in a trailer 
early on Dec. 7 after neighbors reported hearing gun shots. 
</P>
<P>
 Investigators are trying to determine the relationship between the two 
suspects and the victims, Thomas said.NANCY HSU 
