</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By BERT ELJERA 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 The city's business outlook and what it has to offer prospective businesses 
will be discussed from 8:30 a.m. to noon today in the Community Services 
Building, 8200 Westminster Blvd. 
</P>
<P>
 Mayor Charles V. Smith, local developers and business leaders will discuss 
current and planned projects, leasing opportunities and the role of the 
Redevelopment Agency in development projects. 
</P>
