<TEXT>
<P>
 Sprucing Up: The Airporter Garden Hotel is getting a new name to go along with 
its new look. 
</P>
<P>
 The hotel on MacArthur Boulevard in Irvine will become the Atrium Marquis 
Hotel when its $4.5-million renovation is completed next month.All of the 
