<P>
MAN HELD IN DEATH OF TRAVEL AGENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A 30-year-old Glendale man has been arrested in connection with the slaying of 
a travel agent found shot to death in her office last week, police said Monday. 
</P>
<P>
 Garen Zakarian was arrested about 6 p.m. Friday at his home in the 400 block 
of West Wilson Avenue and charged with the murder of Benita Mikailian, said 
police spokesman Chahe Keuroghelian.Police do not have a motive for the 
