<DOCNO> LA101194-0227 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 087676 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
October 11, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
